In [6]:
class MyDataset(Dataset):
    def __init__(self,df,is_train=True,transform=None):
        self.df = df
        self.is_train = is_train
        self.transform = transform
    def __getitem__(self, index):
        if self.is_train:
            img_name = self.df.loc[index,"path"]
            label = self.df.loc[index,"label"]
            image = Image.open(img_name).convert('RGB')
            if self.transform is not None:
                image=self.transform(image)
            return image,torch.from_numpy(np.array(label))
        else:
            img_name = self.df.loc[index,"path"]
            image = Image.open(img_name).convert('RGB')
            if self.transform is not None:
                image=self.transform(image)
            return image
    def __len__(self): 
        return len(self.df)

In [8]:
class MyNet(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, num_class):
        super(MyNet, self).__init__()
        # 加载与训练模型
        model = EfficientNet.from_name('efficientnet-b3') 
        model.load_state_dict(torch.load('../input/cat-dog-config/动物图片识别/model/efficientnet-b3-5fb5a3c3.pth'))
        in_fea = model._fc.in_features
        model._fc = nn.Linear(in_features=in_fea, out_features= num_class, bias=True)
        self.resnet = model
        
    def forward(self, img):        
        out = self.resnet(img)
        return out

In [13]:
model = MyNet(num_class=len(lb.classes_))
criterion = nn.CrossEntropyLoss()
optimizer = torch.optim.AdamW(model.parameters(), lr=lr)

# 将模型放到cuda上
if use_gpu == True:
    model.cuda()
    criterion.cuda()
In [14]:
best_acc = 0.0
for epoch in range(epoch_nums):
    if epoch > 0 and epoch % 8 == 0:
        for param_group in optimizer.param_groups:
            param_group['lr'] = param_group['lr'] * lr_decay
    model.train()
    loss_sum = 0
    nb_tr_steps = 0
    start_time = time.time()
    for inputs, labels in train_loader:
        inputs, labels = inputs.to(device), labels.to(device)
        outputs = model(inputs)
        loss = criterion(outputs, labels)
        loss_sum += loss.item()
        
        nb_tr_steps += 1
        if (nb_tr_steps-1) % 50 == 0:
            loss_step = loss_sum / nb_tr_steps
            print(f"Training loss per 50 training steps: {loss_step}")
        
        optimizer.zero_grad()
        loss.backward()
        optimizer.step()
    torch.cuda.empty_cache()
    
    model.eval()
    with torch.no_grad():
        val_acc = 0.0
        total = 0
        for x, y in val_loader:
            x, y = x.to(device), y.to(device)
            outputs = model(x)
            _, predicted = torch.max(outputs.data, 1)
            total += y.shape[0]
            val_acc += (predicted == y).sum()
    if val_acc.item() > best_acc:
        best_acc = val_acc.item()
        torch.save(model.state_dict(), './mynet.pt')
    print('epoch: %d, train loss: %.03f, val acc: %.03f, time cost: %.1f sec' % (epoch + 1, loss_sum / len(train_loader), val_acc.item() / total, time.time() - start_time))

test_path = os.listdir(path)

test_df = pd.DataFrame(test_path,columns = ["path"])

transforms_test=transforms.Compose([
    transforms.Resize([224, 224]),  
    transforms.ToTensor(),               #将数据转换成Tensor型
    transforms.Normalize((0.485, 0.456, 0.406), (0.229, 0.224, 0.225))])
test_loader = torch.utils.data.DataLoader(
        MyDataset(df=test_df,
                is_train=False,
                transform=transforms_test)
        , batch_size=1, shuffle=False, num_workers=0, pin_memory=False
    )

from tqdm import tqdm
t1 = time.time()
model.eval()
sunmit_preds = []
with torch.no_grad():
    for inputs in tqdm(test_loader):
        inputs = inputs.to(device)
        outputs = model(inputs)
        _, predicted = torch.max(outputs.data, 1)
        sunmit_preds.append(predicted.item())
print(f"Predict time: {time.time() - t1}")
